{"hca204a63gf0a6g4d62g9925g12b71f45e0df": ["Stop - stop! Just take 'im.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "abe35813-ee50-cd07-7c73-6128a3e3e51d"], "h67b9e407g8e88g4a28gb9e2ge686f4225e23": ["That body's all yours - just leave us alone!", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "2465bae0-ffd9-caaf-98ee-e6c223931e18"], "hec93a4b8g9905g476bgaa69g0d20f7b21f7d": ["Stop pesterin' us, freakshow.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "3179e4aa-6a25-f700-b7cb-dfa301399a51"], "he9c6eb5ag47edg48a9ga427g8fafd994c78d": ["Stop pesterin' us, y'old fogey.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "3179e4aa-6a25-f700-b7cb-dfa301399a51"], "h5f37a238g012ag47ebg84c4g386d1a1f4b94": ["Ugh. You look like you've been kissin' a worg's backside.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "909130a1-6884-0355-7c99-aa6d1962d61a"], "hfc368c82gcb44g41ebgb841gd476c4be58fd": ["Piss off, or you'll end up like this bleeder.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "c8715c70-ae58-e378-fa85-3152baa7c4ff"], "ha2541aa1g8c4eg47d4g91dcg68fc580b47ef": ["Keep threatening me. See what happens.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "05f4bc42-8b85-c0a7-769d-b93f9eabae38"], "h8b4e7700gcaceg4246gbe04g6d3c8ed5ea70": ["Oh,  you're <i>real</i> tough. Bullying a kid.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "1812cca4-f06e-9a34-c4ce-13beb6bf3a2c"], "ha52474fag2b28g43d0gb634g7aa3cbc75b1f": ["Sod off or I'll fetch my mum. She was tough as worg-meat <i>before</i> the Absolute came along.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "0f1a8ef0-0b1e-868f-2068-364699b1421d"], "hba051aedg9709g4e08ga94dg4be0d660a3a8": ["Now... she could punch out a dragon!", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "388e0fe2-891d-8d81-1f6e-e7986dfd4c58"], "hc774567eg3a6cg4a4bga3aeg86a1f192fa06": ["Sorry - I don't want any trouble.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "7dc3f0ed-0bde-65fd-0dae-5663bdfd5cfa"], "h43849366ga6f4g4dc6gad27gbb8be9da008f": ["Yeah, too right.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "90d550af-1cbe-39a7-5686-5226571bc54d"], "he1aa80c7gff48g411cg971ag7369213f45bf": ["So don't go startin' nothin'.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "ec172596-315d-a16a-1b44-280dd516b156"], "h08ca839egc7beg4aafgaf41g9a15c908873f": ["Who's the dead man?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "90bb03ae-ffd1-aa5d-5835-3337f4b1d061"], "h4636e543gb225g4ad1gaefag96ffc63c23b2": ["Don't matter who he was. He ain't nothin' but a stain now. ", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "9a382a38-5f02-8c68-69c6-3fba5f2031ab"], "h6d250d03g7aacg492dg82cagf9d3f06236f1": ["Jus' like you'll be if you don't clear off.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "e0e005a2-adfc-d21c-aff5-02bab5f3bcf0"], "h45fd3d68gf632g49e3ga101gfc7d27861857": ["A warning, <i>whelp</i>. Do not threaten me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "2d56106f-b722-c75a-467f-f1527df0dd5d"], "hf82452e3gd390g4165gacb6g9c09c0175bda": ["Whatcha gonna do about it? Run off and cry to yer spider-mum?", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "6f54f1fe-5468-5a9e-8b02-05d1f6670132"], "hf6929e73gf0a2g4206gb13ag2074f79eaed5": ["No. I'm going to cut out your tongue.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "175f90e1-bfc8-418b-3738-8771019c1a82"], "h345a550bgce27g4963g9c66gbff33cf33aee": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "a43f8221-e1f4-c1b3-2c79-704967ad25d4"], "h9e49478dg228bg40e6g83a4gd2af031f43d7": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "c91aec8a-826a-0432-b9d1-e729554eac11"], "hce8f5115gbea5g40e8g9af3gb0697f487e2b": ["Anuvver dirt-elf come to boss us around, eh? Bet I could break your face.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "c0854825-d5d7-8cd4-807b-cc302d45a9cd"], "h2f90c7c7g014bg4eacg9c2ag7b9cbd7af451": ["You look like you think you're hard. Mess with us, and you'll end up like this bleeder.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "7bd472fb-0f2e-7020-fdfc-a40ca10a8083"], "h948a8925g98f2g4aa6g8c6bg6d1d7c92a2c5": ["Wot are you s'posed to be? You look like a dead elf wot got left out in the sun for too long. ", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "03a85abe-318a-fa8c-a82f-8aeec73ad4bd"], "he1d0c35fg82fag4929ga4acgc682427ef9b9": ["I am an alien warrior from another plane of existence.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "5339edfa-defd-b4d0-1859-61c00b715b91"], "h5342519dga848g4d96g802dgf3245ac36c80": ["Sure you are. An' I'm king of the hobgoblins.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "f719dc19-2c7b-4355-e988-2bb0c685a778"], "h24d0a061g2360g4cd7gb345g6cd956207d6f": ["I'm a githyanki; a stranger to this land.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "abec1405-7c80-659f-e882-bee5967ecaf4"], "h6804c1d9g03edg478fg8e1cg36ec45f1e7ed": ["There's plenty of weirdoes about - you'll fit right in, freakshow.", "c8de613d-be02-42ab-ae91-3ed7ba5edafa", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "47aee31d-7234-a1a9-46bf-5ab55850ffea"], "hff3442a3g9074g479fga245gc81eb3395adb": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_GoblinKid000.html", "555a2f30-e39d-cd78-b226-b6eeee54a1f5"]}